<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
<title>Northwood ERP — Start here</title>
<style>
  :root {
    --bg: #0e1117; --surface: #161b22; --elevated: #1c2230; --border: #2a3140;
    --text: #e6edf3; --muted: #8b949e; --secondary: #c9d1d9;
    --accent: #4493f8; --accent-soft: #16263f; --accent-hover: #3b82e0;
    --ok: #3fb950; --code-bg: #1b2330;
  }
  * { box-sizing: border-box; }
  body {
    margin: 0; min-height: 100vh; background: var(--bg); color: var(--text);
    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
    line-height: 1.6; font-size: 15px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; padding: 2rem 1.25rem;
  }
  .card {
    width: 100%; max-width: 680px; background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 14px; padding: 2.5rem 2.5rem 2rem;
  }
  .brand { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: .65rem; font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.05rem; }
  .brand .mark {
    width: 32px; height: 32px; border-radius: 8px; background: var(--accent);
    color: #fff; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.1rem;
  }
  h1 { font-size: 1.85rem; margin: 1.4rem 0 .4rem; letter-spacing: -.01em; }
  .lead { color: var(--secondary); margin: 0 0 .4rem; }
  .sub { color: var(--muted); font-size: 14px; margin: 0; }
  h2 { font-size: .8rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .06em; color: var(--muted);
       margin: 2rem 0 .75rem; font-weight: 600; }
  ol { padding-left: 0; list-style: none; counter-reset: step; margin: 0; }
  ol li {
    counter-increment: step; position: relative; padding: .15rem 0 1rem 2.6rem; margin: 0;
  }
  ol li:last-child { padding-bottom: .25rem; }
  ol li::before {
    content: counter(step); position: absolute; left: 0; top: 0;
    width: 1.7rem; height: 1.7rem; border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--accent-soft); border: 1px solid #284a72; color: #9ecbff;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700;
  }
  ol li b { color: var(--text); }
  code { background: var(--code-bg); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 5px;
         padding: .08em .42em; font-size: .86em; }
  .actions { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: .75rem; margin: 2rem 0 .5rem; }
  a.btn {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: .5rem; text-decoration: none;
    padding: .7rem 1.25rem; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 14.5px; transition: background .15s, border-color .15s;
  }
  a.btn.primary { background: var(--accent); color: #fff; }
  a.btn.primary:hover { background: var(--accent-hover); }
  a.btn.secondary { background: transparent; color: var(--secondary); border: 1px solid var(--border); }
  a.btn.secondary:hover { border-color: var(--accent); color: var(--text); }
  .foot { margin-top: 1.6rem; padding-top: 1.1rem; border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
          color: var(--muted); font-size: 13px; }
  .foot b { color: var(--secondary); }
</style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="card">
    <div class="brand"><span class="mark">N</span> Northwood ERP</div>

    <h1>Welcome — let's get you started.</h1>
    <p class="lead">A self-contained <b>event-driven microservices ERP</b>: seven services coordinating order-to-cash, procure-to-pay, and make-to-stock through Sagas, an outbox/inbox event bus, and real Keycloak sign-in.</p>
    <p class="sub">This is a hands-on demo — drive it yourself in the browser. Here's the quickest way in.</p>

    <h2>Start here</h2>
    <ol>
      <li><b>Click "Enter the ERP" below.</b> You'll be sent to the Keycloak sign-in screen — the demo uses real login, not a bypass.</li>
      <li><b>Sign in. Every persona's password is the same as its username.</b> A friendly first login is <code>sarah</code> / <code>sarah</code> — a sales clerk who can place orders and watch them fulfil end-to-end.</li>
      <li><b>Open the Demo Guide</b> for the full cast (13 personas, each a different role) and ten step-by-step walkthroughs. You can reopen it any time from the <b>?</b> icon in the app's top bar.</li>
      <li><b>Switch persona</b> whenever you like: sign out (top-right) and sign back in as someone else — the UI re-reads your role automatically.</li>
    </ol>

    <div class="actions">
      <a class="btn primary" href="${ERP_URL}">Enter the ERP →</a>
      <a class="btn secondary" href="${ERP_URL}/help.html">Open the Demo Guide</a>
    </div>

    <p class="foot">First time with Northwood? Start with the <b>Demo Guide</b> — it walks you through placing an order, building it on the production floor, and paying for it, one persona at a time.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
